## Import Alias
Always use @/ for imports from src/. Relative paths are forbidden.

CORRECT: import Hero from "@/components/sections/Hero.astro"
WRONG:   import Hero from "../components/sections/Hero.astro"

---

## Styling
CORRECT: class="bg-background text-foreground"
CORRECT: class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground"
WRONG:   class="bg-white text-gray-900"
WRONG:   class="bg-blue-500"
WRONG:   style="padding: 80px"

Use semantic CSS variable classes that work in both light and dark mode.
Never hardcode colors. Never use inline styles.
All global styles go in src/styles/globals.css only.

---

## Responsive Design — Mobile-First
CORRECT: text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl
WRONG:   text-6xl sm:text-3xl

Verify at: 375px (mobile), 768px (tablet), 1024px (laptop), 1280px (desktop)
Requirements: no horizontal overflow, touch targets min 44px, grids stack on mobile

---

## File Types
.astro — use for everything static: sections, pages, layouts, UI (default choice)
.tsx   — use ONLY when client-side state is needed (forms, modals, dropdowns)

---

## File Naming
Components:    PascalCase  — Hero.astro, PricingTable.astro, ThemeToggle.astro
Pages:         kebab-case  — index.astro, about-us.astro, privacy-policy.astro
UI components: kebab-case  — button.tsx, card.tsx, dialog.tsx
Utilities:     camelCase   — utils.ts

---

## Project Structure
src/
  components/
    sections/     Pre-built page sections (Hero, CTA, Pricing, FAQ, Features, etc.)
    ui/           shadcn/ui React components (Button, Card, Dialog, etc.)
  layouts/        BaseLayout, FullWidthLayout, MinimalLayout, AuthLayout, ArticleLayout
  pages/          File-based routing — index.astro = /
  content/        Astro Content Collections — blog posts
  styles/
    globals.css   Design tokens + Tailwind @theme — edit colors here
  lib/
    utils.ts      cn() helper and utilities
public/           Static assets (fonts, favicon, images)
astro.config.mjs  Astro + Vite configuration

