## TypeScript Props — Always Required
Every component needs a typed Props interface:

interface Props {
  title: string;
  description?: string;
  variant?: 'default' | 'centered' | 'wide';
}
const { title, description, variant = 'default' } = Astro.props;

---

## Layout Selection
BaseLayout      → content pages, blog posts (boxed, max-w-5xl)
FullWidthLayout → showcase, gallery, portfolio (full viewport)
MinimalLayout   → 404, maintenance, standalone landing pages (no nav)
AuthLayout      → login, signup, password reset (split screen with branding)
ArticleLayout   → blog articles (reading-optimized typography)

