## Self-Audit Prompts
Portable quality checks in `system/prompts/`. Can be used in any tool via copy-paste.

## Never Do
- Relative imports (use @/ alias)
- Hardcoded colors (use CSS variable classes)
- Inline styles (use Tailwind classes)
- tailwind.config.js or tailwind.config.mjs
- @astrojs/tailwind integration
- HSL or hex colors in @theme (use OKLCH)
- import { z } from 'astro:content' (use astro/zod)
- <ViewTransitions /> (use <ClientRouter />)
- .tsx files for static content (use .astro)
- TypeScript any type
- Skipping responsive design
- Styles outside src/styles/globals.css

